  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use a hostile creature's body as leverage for yourself, allowing you to counter and use their strike as a pivot point for your own. Increase your AC by +4 for the triggering attack. If this would cause the attack to miss, you can make an Attack of Opportunity against them as a part of the same action with a +1 to its critical threat range.</p><p>On a successful hit, the target creature takes your weapon's damage and is knocked 15 feet away from you and makes a Strength Saving Throw, falling Prone and becoming Dazed until the end of their next turn on a failure.</p>",
